<h3>Sencha Touch 2 &mdash; Built for Amazing Apps</h3>

<p>From gmail at 2012-03-08</p>

<p>We&#39;re proud to announce the most advanced version of our industry-leading mobile app framework, Sencha Touch. Sencha Touch 2 is a high-performance HTML5 framework that lets developers create amazing, cross-browser, cross-platform mobile apps.</p>

<p>With an all-new MVC architecture, incredibly smooth scrolling and animations, and an adaptive layout engine, you&rsquo;ll develop rich web apps that rival native technology. Plus, Sencha Touch 2 now provides native packaging, which lets you access device-layer APIs and wrap your app for distribution on app stores.</p>

