<h2>How-tos</h2>

<h3>How to&nbsp;deploy sencha-touch-all.js instead of sencha-touch.js?</h3>

<p>2012-06-21 14:47</p>

<p>Just open PROJECT_HOME/app.json and change sencha-touch.js to sencha-touch-all.js in &quot;js&quot; section.</p>

<pre>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &quot;js&quot;: [
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &quot;path&quot;: &quot;sdk/sencha-touch.js&quot;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; },
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &quot;path&quot;: &quot;app.js&quot;,
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &quot;bundle&quot;: true,&nbsp; /* Indicates that all class dependencies are concatenated into this file when build */
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &quot;update&quot;: &quot;delta&quot;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ],</pre>

<h2>Error messages</h2>

<h3>Uncaught TypeError: Object [object Object] has no method &#39;getDockedItems&#39;</h3>

<p>replace:</p>

<pre>
cards.listCard.getDockedItems()[0].setTitle(...);</pre>

<p>with:</p>

<pre>
cards.listCard.items.items[0].setTitle(...);</pre>

<h3>[WARN][Anonymous] [Ext.Loader] Synchronously loading &#39;Ext.dataview.List&#39;; consider adding &#39;Ext.dataview.List&#39; explicitly as a require of the corresponding class</h3>

<p>2012-05-07 02:06 星期一</p>

<p>解决办法，在 app.js 中加入如下行。</p>

<pre>
​Ext.application({
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; name: &#39;finance&#39;,

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; requires: [
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;Ext.MessageBox&#39;,//
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;Ext.dataview.List&#39;,//
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ...
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ],</pre>

<p>2012-05-27 09:18 星期天 finance project</p>

<h3>TypeError: &#39;undefined&#39; is not a function (evaluating &#39;this.getFullYear()&#39;)</h3>

<p>这个错误通常是由于类似 Ext.Date.format(dt, &#39;Y-m-d&#39;) 这样的代码中，dt 不是 Date 类型引起的。</p>

<h2>Usage cases</h2>

<h3>Ext.form.Panel</h3>

<p><a href="http://localhost/sencha-touch-2.0.1/docs/#!/api/Ext.form.Panel-method-getValues">getValues</a>(&nbsp;<a href="http://localhost/sencha-touch-2.0.1/docs/#!/api/Boolean">Boolean</a>&nbsp;enabled&nbsp;) :&nbsp;<a href="http://localhost/sencha-touch-2.0.1/docs/#!/api/Object">Object</a></p>

<p>Returns an object containing the value of each field in the form, keyed to the field&#39;s name. For groups of checkbox fields with the same name, it will be arrays of values.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><a href="http://localhost/sencha-touch-2.0.1/docs/#!/api/Ext.form.Panel-method-setValues">setValues</a>(&nbsp;<a href="http://localhost/sencha-touch-2.0.1/docs/#!/api/Object">Object</a>&nbsp;values&nbsp;) :&nbsp;<a href="http://localhost/sencha-touch-2.0.1/docs/#!/api/Ext.form.Panel">Ext.form.Panel</a></p>

<p>Sets the values of form fields in bulk.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h3>Ext.field.Text</h3>

<p>不设置 label 则不显示 label。</p>

<p>不设置 name 会使得 Ext.form.Panel.getValues() 的结果中出现 &#39;null&#39; 键值</p>

<pre>
{
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; id : &#39;field-desc&#39;,
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; xtype : &#39;textfield&#39;,
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; label : &#39;Description&#39;,
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; placeHolder : &#39;Trade description&#39;
}</pre>

<h3>Ext.data.Store</h3>

<p>Ext.data.Store.grouper 配合 Ext.dataview.List.grouped = true 来实现分组</p>

<pre>
grouper: {
    groupFn: function(record) {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;    return record.get(&#39;last_name&#39;).substr(0, 1);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sortProperty: &#39;last_name&#39;
}</pre>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<pre>
userStore = Ext.create(&#39;Ext.data.Store&#39;, {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; model: &#39;User&#39;,
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; data: [
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {firstName: &#39;Ed&#39;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; lastName: &#39;Spencer&#39;},
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {firstName: &#39;Tommy&#39;, lastName: &#39;Maintz&#39;},
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {firstName: &#39;Aaron&#39;, lastName: &#39;Conran&#39;},
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {firstName: &#39;Jamie&#39;, lastName: &#39;Avins&#39;}
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ]
});


Ext.regStore(&quot;businesses&quot;, {
model: &#39;Business&#39;,
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; autoLoad: true,
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy: {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; // call Yelp to get business data
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; type: &#39;scripttag&#39;,
